Kaduna State Government has imposed a 24-hour curfew in Atyap Chiefdom of Zangon Kataf Local Government and Chawai Chiefdom in Kauru local government with immediate effect. In a statement issued by Commissioner of Internal Security and Home Affairs,Samuel Aruwan, on Thursday, said that ‘’security agencies are containing the tensions arising from a clash last week over a farmland in Zangon-Kataf. The Commissioner explained that, community leaders had tried to ease the tension which seems to have escalated.